scopecontent.p:
This is a collection of the records of the Philadelphia Academy of Surgery.
                    Materials include minutes, attendance lists, agendas, programs, reports,
                    memoirs, and correspondence related to annual Council and regular meetings;
                    records of conjoint meetings with the New York Surgical Society and others;
                    fellowship applications, including proposals, curricula vitae, and photographs;
                    and subject files of the secretary of the Academy, including files on
                    accreditation, constitution and by-laws, vendors, and applicants not approved
                    for fellowship. There are also several photographs of members of the
                    Academy.
